Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Oh Miyako, why do you torment me too?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: She's stubborn. No matter how many times we knock her down, she keeps getting back up.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: She manipulates her own body with her magic. She controls her own body like a doll.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: I saved you. So why...?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I am grateful to you for bringing me up. If it wasn't for goshujin-sama, I would have died outside the house.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But, goshujin-sama? You are no longer allowed to stay in this mansion.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Don't be silly! This is my house!

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: It's my home, and my children's home...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: How many of those children have you sent to their deaths? Many dolls were sacrificed to stop you.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: And yet those dolls don't hold a grudge against you. Dolls love people. Those dolls think of goshujin-sama as a person until now.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: What are you talking about? I am a human being.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: No, you are not. You are a demon. Goshujin-sama.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You cursed people, kidnapped children and called the Mist. You use sorcery to harm people. No matter what you look like, what would we call you if we didn't call you a demon?

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Don't tell me, you think I'm a demon too, Miyako?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, I do. You are a demon. Goshujin-sama. I think so, Miyabi thinks so too.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But the other dolls were different. They didn't leave goshujin-sama's side. Even when goshujin-sama hurt them, they always thought about you.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: May our oka-sama's suffering cease. May our oka-sama's sadness disappear. That's what we really wished for.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Don't call me oka-sama! I told you to call me goshujin-sama!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Why can't Miyabi and I call you oka-sama?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because Miyabi is a living doll with a will?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because I am a person?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I think, the reason goshujin-sama didn't want us to call you 'oka-sama', is because you were afraid of losing your children again.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: What do you mean?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: That demon is a mother who has lost her child. She tried to summon her children through sorcery, it's probably because she misses her own child.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: May oka-sama be happy. With such wishes, the dolls spent their days in this rough house. Goshujin-sama may have changed, but the hearts of the dolls have not. Do you know why that is?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because you loved them. They all remember your songs. They remember your warmth.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Not a drop of your love has spilled out. The dolls know how wonderful you are as a mother.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: They have been watching you ever since you were a human parent.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Oh, how could this have happened? I kidnapped other people's children and those children don't come back...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Goshujin-sama's form turned into a human form?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: This is her true form. She was already in this demon form when she picked up Miyako, but when she had her two daughters, she had not turned into a monster yet.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: I feel sorry for her. She lived with her two daughters, three of them together, and she lost them both almost at the same time. The dolls encouraged her, but their voices didn't reach her.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Even after she lost her daughters, this person continued to play with her dolls alone. The dolls don't go anywhere. They will always be with her, looking the same. She held on to that thought.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino wonders how she felt when she found Miyako.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako is a living being. She grows up and grows old. She gets sick, she gets injured, and one day she will die.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: What did she think when she found Miyako? What did she say...?
-Whoever left you here was a fool.\n-How could they leave such a beautiful, pure, big girl?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: She looked so happy. It was like finding a treasure.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Oh, where am I supposed to go? Since when did this house become such a scary place?

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: I want to see my daughters. Please return my children to me...

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Miyako, finish this.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Okay.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Miyako, do ya want me to do it?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: No. I'll finish this. That's why I came back here.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yes, ya're right. I said unnecessary things.

Miyako walked up to the monster that has returned to human form, in order to completely bury the owner of Hinayashiki. She uttered an incantation softly, gathered balls of light at her fingertips and pointed them at the owner.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Goodbye.

Name: Hinayashiki Owner
Phrase: Ah, farewell. Miyako.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Have a good rest. Oka-sama.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Hope you see your children over there.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: This house is of sorcery nature. If we don't get out quickly, we'll get caught in it too.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: How are we going to get out? There are no doors leading to the other rooms.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The door is a dummy. There is no hidden door behind the kakejiku either.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It's a sorcery that activates the moment the master of the house disappears. We were right to retreat without defeating her...
Yuuzen, can't you open a Gate here? Even if it deviates slightly from the target point, it would be better than being swallowed by the sorcery as it is.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It's risky, but I have to do it.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Everyone, be prepared. I'm going to cast a Gate forcefully.
Yuuzen tried to release her magic power to create a Gate on the spot. However, for some reason, no magic power can be felt from Yuuzen's hands or body.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Gah... my magic has been sealed.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Me too! I can't use any magic whatsoever!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino's no good either.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: It's okay. My power is effective. And Conductor's power too. I'm sure we can manage with these.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What do you mean, 'we can manage'?

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: If I can transfer Conductor's power into Yuuzen, Yuuzen will be able to use me. Conductor's Iron Injection is more powerful than Yae's magic.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: It's pathetic that I can't use a doll's power without Conductor's help.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But I can't turn my back on ya. Conductor, please lend me your strength. Don't hesitate to put me to the brunt of it.
But Yuuzen, you're not a Train Knight yet. Is it safe to suddenly share my magical power with you?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What are you talking about? I've done it many times with your mother. Stop worrying and get on with it.
If that is the only way, then I have to do it. In order to inject Yuuzen with my magical power, I touched her body with my hands.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: So this is her son's power. That's quite a feat.

Name: Miyabi
Phrase: Yuuzen, it's your turn now. Use me.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yes, please, Miyabihime.
Yuuzen holds the posthumous work of Yuuzen the first, "Miyabihime", and activated her sorcery. It was a very strong power. With this, she would be able to break the curse of Hinayashiki.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Good night. This is the end.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: This is, the summit of Senbon Torii...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I see we're back.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: We were saved by Yuuzen again this time. And, if it wasn't for Miyako, we might not have been able to defeat that thing.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako, you really did your best.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: It was thanks to Yoshino-chan, Yuuzen and everyone else. I couldn't have done it on my own.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I felt once again how helpless I am. I want to be stronger and stronger. To save as many people and dolls as possible.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Hey, Miyako.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What is it? Yoshino-chan.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino's glad you met your oka-san. Glad you met your onee-san.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, that's right. We were able to talk again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Are you happy?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: What do you mean, happy?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Happy to see your family who you've been separated from. Yoshino would be very happy to meet oka-san and otou-san again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino made the cherry blossoms bloom so that Yoshino could meet otou-san and oka-san. It would make it so happy to see my distant family that Yoshino would use a sorcery that's forbidden.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I am happy to see Miyabi, happy...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm also happy to see goshujin-sama, happy...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But why? Why am I crying?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You are happy and sad at the same time. You cried because you said goodbye.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Don't worry. Yoshino is here for you.
Yoshino hugged Miyako, who's confused as to why she was crying.
Even though both of them are not very good with words, they were able to confirm their feelings for each other by attaching their bodies and hearts together in this way.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino is happy. This time we don't have to say goodbye.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino... is your best friend...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan! What's wrong, you suddenly collapsed...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Don't worry. It's just the 'recoil' returning. This happened because I used a strong counter-curse to weaken the effect of the curse your master gave her.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: She won't be able to use sorceries until she recovers. She can't take part in any missions if this happens. Conductor. Yoshino will need some time to recover.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: She also needs the help of a skilled sorceress. Take her to Mount Ooe and have her examined by Shimoamazu the First.
In that case, there's nothing we can do. I'll do as Yuuzen says.
Yoshino, you're dismissed for a while. You did well on this mission.\nTake a good rest and come back when you can use your sorceries again.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yes. Yoshino is a good girl. Will do as Shashou says. Yoshino knew that there would be recoil.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Well, I'm going to leave now. I don't want to get into any more trouble.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Please wait.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What is it? What do ya want from me?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I want to be your apprentice.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Hey, Miyako! What are you talking about out of the blue?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: That's right! Miss Yuuzen is not a member of the SSS, remember?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I want to learn sorcery from you. For the sake of the dolls and for the sake of the people.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: No thanks. Ya have a master, don't cha? Find this Yae doll master. That's the first thing ya should do.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But ya know what, I'll take care of ya once in a while. The Hinayashiki has been neutralized and is still there. As long as I have my Gate, I can always go back there.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Thank you very much. I'd be very grateful if you could help me then.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm happy...

Thus, the incident at Hinayashiki was resolved. Yoshino was dismissed from the frontlines for a while due to the repercussions of the art. The fact that the damage she took was only this small should be considered a good thing.
We were dealing with a very troublesome threat. It is a problem that could not have been solved without Yuuzen. I have to be diligent as the commander of the Special Steel Squad myself.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Nen-nen-korori, nen-korori...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Softly go to sleep.
The Nishikese doll Miyabihime, which Yuuzen was holding when we escaped from Hinayashiki, had already disappeared from Yuuzen's arms by the time we reached the top of the mountain.
